### Class Order Convention

1. Layout: `flex`, `grid`, `block`, `inline`, `relative`, `absolute`
2. Position: `top-0`, `left-0`, `z-10`
3. Box Model: `w-full`, `h-screen`, `m-4`, `p-6`
4. Typography: `text-lg`, `font-bold`, `text-center`
5. Visual: `bg-white`, `border`, `rounded`, `shadow`
6. Interactive: `hover:`, `focus:`, `active:`
7. Responsive: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`

```erb
<!-- Good: Organized class order -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-between w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow md:p-4 sm:flex-col sm:p-2">
```

### Responsive Design

```erb
<!-- Desktop-first approach -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 p-8
            lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-6 lg:p-6
            md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-4 md:p-4
            sm:grid-cols-1 sm:gap-2 sm:p-2">
  <!-- Content -->
</div>

<!-- Typography scaling -->
