</h1>

<!-- Show/hide elements -->
<div class="block md:hidden">Desktop only</div>
<div class="hidden sm:block">Mobile only</div>
```

**Breakpoints**:
- Default (no prefix): 1280px+ (desktop)
- `lg:` - 1024px (laptops)
- `md:` - 768px (tablets)
- `sm:` - 640px (large mobile)

**Responsive Rules**:
- Write desktop styles first (no prefix)
- Add tablet styles with `md:` prefix
- Add mobile styles with `sm:` prefix
- Scale down: `text-5xl md:text-4xl sm:text-3xl`
- Scale spacing: `p-8 md:p-6 sm:p-4`

